title: Baking Set – 6 Piece – Deluxe Non Stick Black Coating Inside and Outside – Carbon Steel Bakeware Set – PFOA PFOS and PTFE Free by Bakken
features: BAKING SET – upgrade your tired and worn bakeware with our 6 piece set. It is restaurant quality, made from flexible and nonstick carbon steel and is commercial grade to ensure longevity and premium results. For your complete peace of mind, we have ensured that every piece of bakeware is PFOA, PFOS and PTFE free

SIZE INFORMATION – there are 6 items included in the set. Roasting pan measuring 14.37 x 9.65 x 1.97 inches, a medium cookie sheet measuring 14.57 x 10.23 x 0.6 inches, 2 round cake pans measuring 10.04 x 8.66 x 1.97 inches, a loaf pan measuring 10 x 5.75 x 2.25 inches and a 12 cup muffin pan measuring 13.8 x 10.4 x 1.18 inches. All items have a thickness of 0.5mm

PREMIUM QUALITY – durable and reliable, all items in the nonstick cookware set feature an attractive and stylish non-stick Black silicone coating. All pieces of bakeware are long lasting, stain resistant and space saving thanks to the stackable wide tray pan design meaning they won’t take up lots of room in your kitchen cabinets

SUITABLE FOR A RANGE OF BAKES – roast meat in the roasting pan, make cookies on the cookie sheet, bake double tiered cakes, create delicious loaves and try your hand at yummy muffins. There are so many options when baking with our non-stick cookware set that you’ll be spoilt for choice

EASY CLEAN – completely dishwasher safe but we recommend handwashing for the best results. The pans and cookie sheet are suitable for the oven, refrigerator and freezer making them perfect for a range of your favorite recipes plus new ones too!
